  "instructions": [
    "In a large pot, heat the oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion, garlic, and ginger, and cook until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add the lentils, turmeric, yellow food coloring, and salt, and stir to combine.",
    "Add the water to the pot, and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low, cover, and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "Stir the lentils occasionally to prevent sticking.",
    "After 20 minutes, remove the pot from the heat, and let it cool slightly.",
    "Serve the lentils hot, garnished with chopped fresh herbs if desired."
